{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDM2MTE0Mzk2", "number": 2597, "title": "[dependencies] Fix issue #2594, update exec-maven-plugin everywhere", "bodyText": "Describe the PR\nexec-maven-plugin is aligned in all the project\n\nRelated issues\n\n\nFixes #2594\n\nReady?\n\n\n Added unit tests for fixed bug/feature\n Passing all unit tests\n Complete build ./mvnw clean verify passes (checked automatically by travis)\n Added (in-code) documentation (if needed)", "createdAt": "2020-06-17T21:49:58Z", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2597", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "b2ca7003285a972e7469010c968ab4f1b255b41f"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-07-16T16:51:48Z", "author": {"login": "KroArtem"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 8, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcsRBqSgH2gAyNDM2MTE0Mzk2OjJiODgyZTg2NTVmMTJkOTIzM2Q1MTg3NjBiYmRlYjNiZDZmYTY0ZmU=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc1iFVYAH2gAyNDM2MTE0Mzk2OjU5YWNkNmQ5NjljN2JjYTQ4OTY5YmI1NTRjZjFlYzdlMDBhOTE3ZjI=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "2b882e8655f12d9233d518760bbdeb3bd6fa64fe", "author": {"user": {"login": "KroArtem", "name": "Artem"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/2b882e8655f12d9233d518760bbdeb3bd6fa64fe", "committedDate": "2020-06-17T21:48:57Z", "message": "fix issue #2594, update exec-maven-plugin everywhere"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDMzMDM2Mjcx", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2597#pullrequestreview-433036271", "createdAt": "2020-06-18T08:04:39Z", "commit": {"oid": "2b882e8655f12d9233d518760bbdeb3bd6fa64fe"}, "state": "CHANGES_REQUESTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 3, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNi0xOFQwODowNDo0MFrOGlkJHw==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNi0xOFQwODowODo0NFrOGlkSSA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ0MjA0MjY1NQ==", "bodyText": "I think, we should check, whether this profile actually still works and whether this is documented.\nThe goal was, if I remember correctly, to easily start the designer from the current workspace like\ncd pmd-apex\n./mvnw -Pdesigner org.codehaus.mojo:exec-maven-plugin:java\n# or ./mvnw -Pdesigner org.codehaus.mojo:exec-maven-plugin:exec ??\n\nI'm not sure, whether this still works, since the designer is maybe not on the classpath? And it is anyway in a different repository (https://github.com/pmd/pmd-designer)...\nTo start the designer, one should follow the instructions on https://github.com/pmd/pmd/wiki/Setup-IDE\nI'd suggest to remove this profile completely", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2597#discussion_r442042655", "createdAt": "2020-06-18T08:04:40Z", "author": {"login": "adangel"}, "path": "pmd-apex/pom.xml", "diffHunk": "@@ -105,7 +105,7 @@\n           <plugin>", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "2b882e8655f12d9233d518760bbdeb3bd6fa64fe"}, "originalPosition": 1}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ0MjA0MzA1Mw==", "bodyText": "Let's define the version in the main parent pom under \"pluginManagment\" and remove the explicit version here in pmd-doc", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2597#discussion_r442043053", "createdAt": "2020-06-18T08:05:22Z", "author": {"login": "adangel"}, "path": "pmd-doc/pom.xml", "diffHunk": "@@ -24,7 +24,7 @@\n                     <plugin>\n                         <groupId>org.codehaus.mojo</groupId>\n                         <artifactId>exec-maven-plugin</artifactId>\n-                        <version>1.6.0</version>\n+                        <version>3.0.0</version>", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "2b882e8655f12d9233d518760bbdeb3bd6fa64fe"}, "originalPosition": 5}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ0MjA0NTAwMA==", "bodyText": "It looks like this should be refactored and reused. We could define a function in .travis/common-functions.sh - then we have in the future only one place, where we need to update the plugin version.\nOn a side note: The goal of this is, to figure out, which version we are currently building. Calling the exec-maven-plugin is one way to do this, which works, but it's very heavy (starting maven to only read the <version> element of the pom.xml file....). Maybe you know a better way to read/parse the version from the file in the shell?", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2597#discussion_r442045000", "createdAt": "2020-06-18T08:08:44Z", "author": {"login": "adangel"}, "path": ".travis/build-coveralls.sh", "diffHunk": "@@ -4,7 +4,7 @@ set -e\n source .travis/logger.sh\n source .travis/common-functions.sh\n \n-VERSION=$(./mvnw -q -Dexec.executable=\"echo\" -Dexec.args='${project.version}' --non-recursive org.codehaus.mojo:exec-maven-plugin:1.5.0:exec)\n+VERSION=$(./mvnw -q -Dexec.executable=\"echo\" -Dexec.args='${project.version}' --non-recursive org.codehaus.mojo:exec-maven-plugin:3.0.0:exec)", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "2b882e8655f12d9233d518760bbdeb3bd6fa64fe"}, "originalPosition": 5}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "9180b479cb77eeb315ddf78d866d6e280f1b0620", "author": {"user": {"login": "adangel", "name": "Andreas Dangel"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/9180b479cb77eeb315ddf78d866d6e280f1b0620", "committedDate": "2020-07-16T16:20:43Z", "message": "[apex] Remove profile designer, which started the deprecated designer\n\nUsers are encouraged to use https://github.com/pmd/pmd-designer instead."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "bb005ea5d4122bcc49e8599fe5bf3d4c13839024", "author": {"user": {"login": "adangel", "name": "Andreas Dangel"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/bb005ea5d4122bcc49e8599fe5bf3d4c13839024", "committedDate": "2020-07-16T16:21:26Z", "message": "Refactor exec-maven-plugin version and usage"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "34f185b03a41e5df1ed52897cf279c0607dee181", "author": {"user": {"login": "adangel", "name": "Andreas Dangel"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/34f185b03a41e5df1ed52897cf279c0607dee181", "committedDate": "2020-07-16T16:21:26Z", "message": "Use xmlint to get the pom version"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "2adc457d23bb5582a5dae9e94eb955fdfb9ebacf", "author": {"user": {"login": "adangel", "name": "Andreas Dangel"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/2adc457d23bb5582a5dae9e94eb955fdfb9ebacf", "committedDate": "2020-07-16T16:23:37Z", "message": "[doc] Update release notes, refs #2597, fixes #2594"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "17e57633b5a38c1008dfaab6536c9298dd7535da", "author": {"user": {"login": "adangel", "name": "Andreas Dangel"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/17e57633b5a38c1008dfaab6536c9298dd7535da", "committedDate": "2020-07-16T16:25:59Z", "message": "Merge branch 'master' into pr-2597"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "59acd6d969c7bca48969bb554cf1ec7e00a917f2", "author": {"user": {"login": "adangel", "name": "Andreas Dangel"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/commit/59acd6d969c7bca48969bb554cf1ec7e00a917f2", "committedDate": "2020-07-16T16:46:40Z", "message": "Revert \"Use xmlint to get the pom version\"\n\nThis reverts commit 34f185b03a41e5df1ed52897cf279c0607dee181."}}]}}}, "rateLimit": {"limit": 5000, "remaining": 4823, "cost": 1, "resetAt": "2021-11-01T16:37:27Z"}}}